    "order": 1
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_0",
    "text": "As You Read",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.10029850746268656,
      0.04904214559386973,
      0.23243781094527363,
      0.06620689655172414
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_1",
    "text": "Consider a conflict of interest you have encountered in your life. How did you resolve it?",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.0891542288557214,
      0.07172413793103448,
      0.25233830845771144,
      0.14835249042145593
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_3",
    "text": "When you encounter an ethical decision and must choose a course of action, ask yourself these important questions:",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3088557213930348,
      0.07295019157088123,
      0.8453731343283583,
      0.10911877394636016
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_4",
    "text": "• Is it against the law? Does it violate company or professional policies? • Even if everyone is doing it, how would I feel if someone did this to me? • Am I sacrifi cing long-term benefits for short-term gains?",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3255721393034826,
      0.11524904214559387,
      0.8692537313432835,
      0.20904214559386974
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_5",
    "text": "The Ethical Decision-Making Process",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.30646766169154227,
      0.229272030651341,
      0.7530348258706467,
      0.2519540229885057
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_6",
    "text": "Here are some steps to take if you fi nd yourself in an ethical dilemma:",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.3072636815920398,
      0.2550191570881226,
      0.8390049751243781,
      0.2899616858237548
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_7",
    "text": "1. Identify the ethical dilemma. 2. Discover alternative actions. 3. Decide who might be affected. 4. List the probable effects of the alternatives. 5. Select the best alternative.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.32477611940298506,
      0.29670498084291186,
      0.7164179104477612,
      0.389272030651341
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_8",
    "text": "Using this process will enable you to make a more informed ethical choice. Making an ethical decision involves more people than just you.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.30646766169154227,
      0.39846743295019155,
      0.8573134328358208,
      0.4542528735632184
    ],
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6",
    "order": 9
  },
