  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_c04_874768_mt.pdf_6_12",
    "text": "1. What is the difference between personal and business ethics? 2. Describe some of the ways that unethical business practices can affect a business. 3. What is the relationship between illegal behaviors of business and unethical behaviors of business?",
